During the year, the USM-quoted property and hotel group bought a portfolio
of properties from British Land for Pounds 5.35m.
This was financed by the issue of 66m shares.
This, added to purchases made the previous year, gives the company a Pounds
7.5m asset base generating rental income of Pounds 750,000 a year.
