Mill Snack Foods. Following the deal, which will involve a trebling of IMC's
share capital, it is proposing to change its name to Continental Foods.
With operations in Wednesbury, near Birmingham and Waspik in the
Netherlands, Red Mill makes a range of maize and potato-based snacks. In the
year to March 1994 it made an operating profit before non-recurring items of
