Portfolio Foods, Red Mill's parent, will receive Pounds 2.25m in cash and
462.5m new IMC shares, of which 372m have been placed with institutions and
other investors subject to a 10-for-7 open offer at 2p. Trading in the
shares has been suspended at 2 1/2 p.
IMC also announced its figures for the year to April which showed slightly
lower pre-tax profits of Pounds 364,000 (Pounds 377,000) on turnover of
Pounds 6.2m (Pounds 6.1m).
