<HEADLINE>
FT  28 JUL 94 / Jaguar remains in the red
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Jaguar, Ford's UK luxury car subsidiary, remained in the red in the second
quarter with an unchanged operating loss of Dollars 62m. Ford said Jaguar
was expected to return to profit in 1995. The business had shown an
underlying improvement following cost cutting and improved product quality.
Ford of Europe results, Page 23
